description: This tastefully appointed 2 bed 2 bath condo is only two blocks from the beach, 5 minute drive to Seaport and a quick trip to Logan or downtown. Enjoy effortless access to all that Southie has to offer from incredible restaurants, bars and shops to Castle Island and beautiful beaches. A gas fireplace to stay cozy in the winter and the sliding glass door opens your home to a covered rear porch and private fenced in back yard for entertaining in the summer. The renovated kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and flows perfectly to an open dining and living room with recessed lights and in ceiling speakers. This home features all the creature comforts you'd expect from central air conditioning, to a central vac system and a large primary suite with pass through closet and en suite bath. Laundry in unit and abundant storage. All that is missing is you!
